experiment: F-META2 principle extraction gap measurement and structural fix
hypothesis: Principle extraction rate has declined because DOMEX lanes enforce lesson creation but not principle synthesis; a close_lane.py prompt will make the gap visible and increase conversion rate

method.measurement: Count principles extracted from L-550+ window vs total lessons in that window
method.comparison: Historical overall rate (173P/598L = 28.9%) vs recent window (5P/111L = 4.5%)
method.intervention: Added principle-extraction NOTICE to close_lane.py when MERGED lanes have L-NNN but no P-NNN reference
method.proof_of_concept: Extracted P-221/P-222 (S365) then P-223-P-226 (S366) via systematic scan of L-550-L-661. P-218/P-219 expanded with additional citations.
method.scan_method: Agent-assisted scan of 112 lessons (L-550-L-661). Each candidate required >=3 supporting lessons verified against Finding sections. Citation accuracy verified for top candidates: C1 4/5 confirmed, C4 1/5 confirmed (dropped), C5 2/4 confirmed.

new_principles_s366: P-223 (measurement channel coverage — tool scope must match data scope; 5 tools verified)
P-230 (bottleneck migration — protecting one resource shifts collision to next; 4 successive layers)
P-231 (Lamarckian correction immunity — directed correction prevents quality degradation; 4 tests)
P-232 (accumulation scoring exploitation — frequency penalties needed; 4 scoring regimes)
results.note_id_collision: Original P-224/225/226 renumbered to P-230/231/232 due to concurrent session adding P-224-P-229
expanded_principles_s366: P-218 expanded: format IS enforcement mechanism (+5 citations, n=4→10 protocols)
P-219 expanded: generalized from substrate-only to all creation-time checks (+4 citations, n=2→7 cases)

structural_fix.change: Added principle-extraction NOTICE when MERGED lane has L-NNN but no P-NNN in closure text
structural_fix.mechanism: L-601 structural enforcement — making invisible gap visible at the natural decision point

prediction.escalation: if rate stays <10%, upgrade to periodic batch synthesis or blocking enforcement
